column3:
“Was VERY interested in trying this strain, because I kind of have a thing for cherries. I will (shamelessly I might add) get baked and munch on nothing but straight up maraschino cherries. Yeah. I'm that guy. 

So this strain has an AMAZING smell. Unmistakably cherry, with some earthy/woody undertone. It was the first bud to impress me that much on smell alone in quite a while. Very unique.

As far as taste goes, I r...”

“I've tried more than a few strains but this one and Chocolope both delivered euphoria unlike any others. Now that I've tried them, I'm not sure I've ever experienced euphoria with cannabis before. Also the anti-depressive mental shift is significant and endures.”

“The Cherry Cookies Shatter concentrate by FireLine is packed with a cherry flavor and aroma, and when exhaled from your nose it leaves a wonderful cherry after-smell" that is quite sweet and fruity. The high increased my mood and gave me nice body buzz while avoiding a foggy mind. After just a few dabs of this
column4: I would go ahead and put this in my top 10 strains.”"

column3:
“This is a wonderful strain for all my weed enthusiasts who love a good tasting bud with a great high. I mean damnnn the taste is very unique and sweet. Very relaxing and mellow high. I love this strain. Instantly made my Top 5 & Must Try lists... 


Enjoy my fellow smokers!”

“Buds are very attractive in color and smells earthy with a nice sweet flavor.

Amazing experience! This hybrid starts off pretty mellow and uplifting but as the high gets stronger it randomly fluctuated between the body to head high ratios and it was always unpredictable and if you can focus enough you will get really excited to see what it will throw at you next. Also a very long lasting high that gives off great eu...”

“Tightly packed nugs with flavorful smell that jumps into your nose quickly. Upon burning this strain you get a quick frontal lobe high. Smoked 2 small bowls got up and went to bed to think for a few hours. This strain will leave you alone, sitting in a catatonic state, with a very clear mind. For those of you that feel the need to move, be prepared for an olympic weightlifters challenge as this strain left me trying ...”

“Helps with depression, ptsd, and pain management. 
I got a happy and less concerned about the major  stressors around me. Great for doing simple tasks, but nothing to complicated. Sweet taste. Very pungent.  One of my five faves!!!!”

“I was excited about this particular strain because of the two power house strains it comes from, Cherry Pie & Girl Scout Cookies. It felt great. From the 1st hit I felt it immediately. Very potent and it definitely put me in a euphoric state. Super happy with it and I would recommend it to anyone!”
“One of the more relaxing strains I've had. Very euphoric, Very earthy, pretty strain. Strong body high, with a clean smoke.”
“Incredible strain. Instantly uplifting on the exhale. Smooth and tasty. Best version of Girl Scout Cookies I've tried.”
“This one wasn't too much of a standout for me.  Basically made me happy and awake, a little forehead pressure sensation.”
“My body feels amazing”
“1 of my favorite.. strain.. good taste.. good vibe.... focus..in everything.. the world is yours..”
“This strain is exceptional! I've never experienced a more clear headed yet relaxing high. Whenever I smoke this strain I'm super productive and in the best mood!”
“Great for relaxing but doesnt make you pass out”
“Perfect!!!”
“This strain is exceptional! I've never experienced a more clear headed yet relaxing high. Whenever I smoke this strain I'm super productive and in the best mood!”
“Perfect!!!”
“1 of my favorite.. strain.. good taste.. good vibe.... focus..in everything.. the world is yours..”
“Absolutely love this strain. Great in the morning to start your day feeling light and happy”

“I took about four tokes  during the game with my buddy. It was really smooth. It came on easy and held us for a while. Quietly focusing on the game turned to jokes and laughing.  It was actually a great high.  Let’s you down nice and easy.”
“great hybrid between cherry pie and Girl Scout cookies has a great smell and taste with patches of purple great combination between the two”
“is good for imnsonio to”
“Great flavor and fantastic GSC high. A favorite and easy to grow. Cant go wrong with a GSC #420Sweepstakes”
“Love it. Its strong on your body but light on your mind so you feel groovy enough to use it during the day but it wont make you feel any anxiety.”

“The buds that grew from this plant were incredibly fluffy, soft and what I like to refer to as The Kind - a rare, dank sticky strain that’s hard to come by. The Cherry Pie is most evident here, in taste and smell AND effect. It is overwhelmingly sweet, pungent and sharp - You gets hints of the Durban parent too. I react so strongly it smells, i know immediately whether I will like a strain based on its smell. And thi...”

“This is a down right awesome strain. Thanks to the budtender at the reef that gave me a little info on it made the flavors pop hard on the inhale rightous cherry flavor as well as the exhale nice earthy flavor fallowed by the cherry endeing the rip.”
“I like this strain. The taste, buzz was surprisingly kook. But I figured that it would be, belonging to the cookie family. I will get again.”
“Great smell! Potent dense buds.”

“Most def a mood enhancer..had shatter..was smooth you can taste all the flavors of GSC and Cherry Pie it all goes together in this euphoric... I'm down for whateva strain..Great for pain and the connoisseur!!”
“Picked this up simply because it had GSC in it. Probably my favorite GSC cross mix so far. You get super baked but your mind becomes free and clear.”
“One of my best so far, I was walking so happy and had a great head High 9/10”
“I wasn’t to impressed by this strain, which is very unfortunate because I had high hopes for it. Maybe the batch wasn’t up to it’s highest Standards. However the buds were gorgeous”

“The euphoria from this burn was quite refreshing! I haven’t had that feeling in quite sometime. In just a few short pulls the effects were immediate & welcomed. A definite keeper in the starting lineup.”
“🍒🍥The name says it all it starts off fairly sweet like cherries and this concentrate finishes terp doubt like cookies. I'm finding this hybrid even more enjoyable than I thought!🍒🍥”
